vdr-addon-noad (0.6.0-2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Tobias Grimm <tg@e-tobi.net>
    - Depend on Debian's libavcodec-dev instead of C.Marillat's libavcodec1-dev
    - Added 11_ffmpeg-config.dpatch tp patch configure.ac to let autoconf use
      ffmpeg-config (to statically link Debian's ffmpeg)
    - Run autoconf in debian/rules and clean up configure to keep diff small
    - Bumped Standards-Version to 3.6.2
    - Depend on debhelper (>> 4.1.16)
    - Switched to po-debconf
    - Removed shebang lines in R10.noad and S50.noad, because these scripts
      are not executables anyway
    - Fixed email addresses in changelog

